decks.notes: The main strategy of this deck revolves around utilizing the graveyard as a resource to fuel powerful recursion and reanimation effects, while also taking advantage of efficient creature-based aggression. Grist, the Hunger Tide serves as the central commander, enabling the player to repeatedly sacrifice creatures for value and generate insect tokens to overwhelm the opponent. The deck includes a combination of fast mana accelerants, removal spells, and key creatures like Bloodghast, Vengevine, and Yawgmoth, Thran Physician to apply early pressure and maintain a strong board presence. With access to powerful tutors such as Demonic Tutor and Survival of the Fittest, the deck aims to quickly assemble its synergistic pieces and overwhelm the opponent with a relentless onslaught of threats.
